This paper is about natural language processing (NLP) for Arabic language. The most relevant arXiv CS sub-category for this topic is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers research on NLP, text mining, and information retrieval. Other likely sub-categories include cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as these fields are closely related to NLP and often used in Arabic NLP research.
